{
  "stem": "979.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were-- you know, we knew it wouldn't be good-- of what we were seeing-- noise, seeing the trains and everything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, when we got there, that night was the most horrible night I ever spent in-- in my life, you know, I had-- besides these other things came up that were not great.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the fear to see all these people-- what is this?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And immediately, the-- these things so fast, like they came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For instance, they-- they separated us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put the groups like immediately by looking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They won't ask your age, because the-- there's so many people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They don't have time for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then you can say any age you want to, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there they-- they looked at the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, my aunt was about 55 years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And probably she had gray hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that they'd put her with the older people, because they don't need them for working.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why would they keep us there-- the young ones?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's just because they needed us for work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise they would send us all to the gas chambers right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they put them immediately in group with the ladies-- the men separate-- also older men, and they were not that old.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and then they put me, my cousin, my sister, and me-- no, they put me with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It means that they-- they saw me that I was too young to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they put you-- that mean you are for the gas chamber too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they put me with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister saw this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put my cousin with my sister and all the other girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was so much going on there now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my sister saw that I went with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
